}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{The course is designed to show and master the principles of the econometric 
model building with emphasis on results' economic interpretation and 
verification\'2e\line
The course presupposes knowledge of statistics and economics at bachelor 
level\'2e\line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
